(17, 1, '2011-10-29 08:50:41', '2011-10-29 08:50:41', 'Our lighting ranges from small bedside lamps to much larger floor standing lamps designed to make a real statement in a room. We have a selection of chandeliers that add glamour and sparkle to any room. While we have extensive stocks on display in store, if there is something special you are looking for, we can help you track it down', 'Lighting', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'lighting', '', '', '2011-10-29 11:31:10', '2011-10-29 11:31:10', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sandrajane/?page_id=17', 30, 'page', '', 0),
