(19, 1, '2011-10-29 08:51:01', '2011-10-29 08:51:01', 'Our range is always expanding and changing, as we seek out new different items you won’t see in other local stores. From photograph frames to reading glasses, handmade pottery to jewellery, vases to bath oils.\r\n\r\nIf you can’t make up your mind for that special someone, we offer gifts tokens, available for any amount.  We’re also able to help you select a gift, wrap it elegantly and ensure it arrives at its destination on time. If time is precious, we’re just a phone call away.\r\n\r\nOur Wedding List service enables you to create a list and leave it with us to manage.\r\n\r\nWe’re more than just a shop. <a title="Our Services" href="http://localhost/sandrajane/?page_id=21">See how we can help you in other ways.</a>', 'Gifts & Accessories', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gifts-accessories', '', '', '2011-10-29 09:45:08', '2011-10-29 09:45:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sandrajane/?page_id=19', 40, 'page', '', 0),
