(21, 1, '2011-10-29 08:51:27', '2011-10-29 08:51:27', '<strong>A complete service</strong>\r\nYou select from our extensive range of fabrics and we can arrange to make up your curtains, blinds, cushions, bedspreads, loose covers, upholstery and headboards. We’ll fit them all too.\r\n\r\n<strong>Interior design services</strong>\r\nWe''ll advise you on the colours, fabrics and ‘look’ for your home or business. To do that we can first visit you at home or premises and discuss your ideas. Then we’ll use our expertise to combine colours and materials successfully and create the perfect mood for you.\r\n\r\n<strong>Wedding list</strong>\r\nWe''ll help you put together a list from our stylish range of furniture and house wares including rugs, lighting, china, glassware, kitchenware and accessories. Then we’ll keep you posted on its current status.\r\n\r\n<strong>Gift Service\r\n</strong>We can provide you with a beautiful Gift Voucher to any value. Our telephone gift service enables you to discuss your gift idea with us, before we wrap it beautifully and then deliver it with your greetings.\r\n\r\n<strong>Delivery</strong>\r\nWe can deliver to (almost) anywhere in the world. <a href="mailto:contact@sandrajane.co.uk?subject=Delivery%20requirements">Contact us</a> with your requirements.\r\n\r\n<strong>Stay in touch </strong>\r\nIf you''d like to receive our bulletin on new arrivals and special offers, please <a href="mailto:contact@sandrajane.co.uk?subject=I%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20touch.%20My%20special%20interests%20are">send your email</a> and postal address with your special interests to us.\r\n\r\n<strong>Credit cards are welcome\r\n</strong> All major credit cards are accepted except Diners.\r\n\r\n<strong>Shop open </strong>\r\nMonday–Saturday 9.30am-5.30pm', 'Our Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'our-services', '', '', '2011-10-29 09:45:48', '2011-10-29 09:45:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sandrajane/?page_id=21', 90, 'page', '', 0),
