(23, 1, '2011-10-29 08:51:39', '2011-10-29 08:51:39', 'Sandra Jane\r\n46-48 King Street\r\nCambridge CB1 1LN\r\nTel: 01223 323211\r\nFax: 01223 507095\r\n<a href="mailto:contact@sandrajane.co.uk">Email</a><strong>\r\n\r\n</strong>To view a map click <a>here</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Opening hours\r\n</strong>Monday–Saturday\r\n9.30am-5.30pm\r\n\r\nThere is pay-and-display parking in King Street itself and nearby Manor Street and Jesus Lane. Call the shop in advance if you need to pick-up an order outside the shop.\r\n<strong>\r\nCredit cards welcomed\r\n</strong>We accept all major credit cards except Diners\r\n<strong>\r\nYou can''t visit us?\r\n</strong>We can send you details of new arrivals and special offers by mail. Simply send<a href="mailto:contact@sandrajane.co.uk?subject=I%20want%20to%20stay%20in%20touch.%20My%20special%20interests%20are"> your email and postal address, with a note on your special interests. </a>\r\n\r\nDon’t forget to follow our new product ranges on <a>Twitter</a> and <a>Facebook</a>', 'Find Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'find-us', '', '', '2011-10-29 09:46:38', '2011-10-29 09:46:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/sandrajane/?page_id=23', 100, 'page', '', 0),
